sellerCard.oneLiner: UK based Web, Video, and Graphic professional
sellerCard.description:
I have been creating websites, graphics and videos for over 15 years.  I have now become freelance and I would love to share my skills on Fiverr.  

I can create stunning websites, and videos.  

I always aim to provide the best service possible.  

Making people happy, makes me happy.

description.content:
** KINDLY MESSAGE ME FIRST BEFORE MAKING AN ORDER **


I am a UK based Web Design professional.


The packages here are for Brochure Websites. If you require an online shop, car dealer, real estate, booking system or other special functionality website then please contact me for a bespoke gig.  Otherwise, the packages in this gig includes:


 Basic 

·    Fully Functional Online Website (Simple Design)

·    Up to 3 pages (extra pages available on extras)

·    1 year free web hosting (if required)


 Standard 

·    Fully Functional Online Website (Good Quality Design)

·    Mobile & Tablet Friendly

·    Up to 6 pages (extra pages available on extras)

·    1 year free web hosting (if required)

·    Free email setup with Zoho (if required)

·    Logo (if required)

·    Stock Images (my own library)


 Premium 

·    Fully Functional Online Website (Premium Quality Design)

·    Mobile & Tablet Friendly 

·    CMS: Manage / Edit / Add unlimited pages yourself

·    I can create up to 8 pages (but you can add more yourself in the CMS)

·   1 year free web hosting (if required)

·    Free business email setup with Zoho (if required)

·    Logo (if required)

·    Stock Images (my own library)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I use my own web hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes you can, so as long as you have cPanel hosting.  Most hosting companies do provide cPanel.  

Remember, I can always host the website for you free for a year.  I use Memset hosting which is super fast, reliable, and secure.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What happens after your free 1 year web hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
We can provide 1 year free web hosting.   

After 1 year:
To cover the hosting costs with our providers, if you want to continue to have the site hosted with us, we charge £50 a year (around $64 USD).   But this is only optional, if you want us to continue hosting the website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you register my domain?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I can.   Please contact me so we can arrange this with our provider.
